// Anniversary Anim Pack
section
	h2#anim_pack: a.link(href="https://www.nexusmods.com/newvegas/mods/70158", target="_blank") Anniversary Animation Pack
	h2.install Installation instructions:
	ul: li #[b Main Files - Anniversary Anim Pack]
	p Includes three of Hitman's previous animation mods, #[a(href="https://www.nexusmods.com/newvegas/mods/67728", target="_blank") Subtle Camera Motion], #[a(href="https://www.nexusmods.com/newvegas/mods/67760", target="_blank") Iron Sights Recoil Animations], and #[a(href="https://www.nexusmods.com/newvegas/mods/67841", target="_blank") Fire Animation Variants], as well as some new previously unreleased animations.
// Anniversary Anim Pack - General Bugfix
section
	h2#anim_bugfix: a.link(href="https://www.nexusmods.com/newvegas/mods/72320", target="_blank") Anniversary Anim Pack - General Bugfix
	h2.install Installation instructions:
	ul
		li #[b Main Files - AnniAnimPack_BugFix 1.3]
		li #[b Main Files - Bonus Patch] (When prompted, rename to Anniversary Anim Pack - General Bugfix - Bonus Patch)
	p Fixes many bugs/inconsistencies in Anniversary Anims Pack.